    "The settings of other variables are consistent with those in the benchmark regression.",
    "Currently, most scholars measure managers' attention using questionnaires and textual analysis.",
    "The annual reports of listed enterprises provide a good data source to analyze the managers' concerns about environmental issues; therefore, we refer to the environmental lexicon constructed by Chen et al. (2018).",
